title: Guy Eats The Most Tender And Moist Meatloaf He Has Ever Tried | Diners, Drive-Ins & Dives
description:
Guy Fieri goes to a couple of fancy diners in San Diego, California. There, he eats a short-rib French dip and tries out the most tender and moist meatloaf he has ever had in his life.
